## 1. Executive Summary

Tread Intelligence is an end-to-end AI-powered supply chain system built entirely inside Snowflake that transforms Tireco's procurement from reactive (buyers manually deciding what to order) to predictive (the system recommends optimal purchase orders with AI-generated justifications, incorporating weather forecasts, port congestion, economic signals, and ML demand predictions).

**Scale:** 250 SKUs Г— 32 distribution centers Г— 8 vendors Г— 1,200+ customers across 4 US regions.

### Target Business Impact

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Manual forecasting time | -70% reduction |
| Stockout rate (high-demand SKUs) | -50% reduction |
| Overstock carrying costs | -15% reduction |
| Forecast accuracy (MAPE) | <15% |
| Auto-generated PO approval rate | >80% |

