### Accept/Reject Workflow
- Buyer clicks Accept/Reject on a recommendation in the dashboard
- Calls `SP_UPDATE_RECOMMENDATION_STATUS(id, status, reviewer, notes)`
- Updates `RECOMMENDATION_STATUS`, `REVIEWER_ID`, `REVIEWED_AT`, `REVIEWER_NOTES`
- Full audit trail visible in Actions Log tab

